## 6. EXPECTED OUTCOME

The proposed AI-Powered Student Dropout Prediction and Counseling System will provide an intelligent solution for identifying students at risk of dropping out before academic failure occurs. The system will analyze attendance records, academic performance, and behavioral indicators to generate accurate dropout risk predictions.

By utilizing Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning techniques, the platform will help educational institutions provide timely counseling, improve student engagement, reduce dropout rates, enhance academic success, and support informed decision-making through real-time analytics and predictive insights.
